# Generated branding rasters — committed only as SVG sources; the Pages
# workflow renders these PNGs from public/icon.svg + public/og-image.svg
# via rsvg-convert at build time. Generate locally with the same commands
# if you need to verify them.
public/icon-192.png
public/icon-512.png
public/icon-maskable.png
public/og-image.png

